570
00:41:56,184 --> 00:41:59,865
Vivian, I hope
you feel better!

571
00:42:17,824 --> 00:42:21,289
Lock the door
when you leave.

572
00:42:27,201 --> 00:42:30,369
Yeah, I know
the routine.

573
