00:43:40,076 --> 00:43:43,881
So we Hindu?
No beef?

579
00:43:43,882 --> 00:43:46,378
None at all.

580
00:43:47,317 --> 00:43:50,508
Yeah, man.
We're cryogenic.

581
00:43:51,889 --> 00:43:56,292
