586
00:44:08,541 --> 00:44:10,175
I'm gonna put it in my mouth.
I'm gonna be hard.

587
00:44:10,176 --> 00:44:14,346
Call Covonne.
I know exactly where we can go.

588
00:44:14,347 --> 00:44:17,173
Let's get some drinks, yo.

589
00:44:21,920 --> 00:44:28,820
A shift of paradigms.
I drop a pair of dimes in the meter.

590
00:44:41,106 --> 00:44:44,775
That's what I'm
talking about!

591
00:44:47,713 --> 00:44:50,779
Oh. Oh. Oh.
Talent. Talent. Talent.

592
00:44:50,983 --> 00:44:53,518
- Trese!
- Hey.

593
00:44:53,519 --> 00:44:57,457
