guys like experiments

658
00:50:25,162 --> 00:50:30,535
just to prove my hypothesis that all
men have questionable motives.

659
00:50:30,536 --> 00:50:33,905
But I promise I won't treat you
like one of my guinea pigs.

660
00:50:33,906 --> 00:50:35,705
Thank you.

661
00:50:35,706 --> 00:50:37,576
So what are you
going to do for me?

662
00:50:37,577 --> 00:50:42,474
Um, let's go
shoe shopping.

663
00:50:42,480 --> 00:50:46,318
