669
00:51:07,039 --> 00:51:10,343
He pulled a 4-9-0
and got locked up.

670
00:51:10,344 --> 00:51:12,577
Shut up.
Jimmy killed somebody?

671
00:51:12,578 --> 00:51:19,183
You need to revisit the teachings
of the good Dr. Dre. That's a 1-8-7.

672
00:51:19,352 --> 00:51:21,435
What's a 4-9-0?

673
00:51:21,436 --> 00:51:23,588
Shoplifting.

674
00:51:23,589 --> 00:51:27,087
